<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>COSMOS DAILY | APOD</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>

  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"/>

  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #0D0D0D;
      color: #EAEAEA;
    }

    .main-container {
      margin-top: 60px;
      background-color: #1A1A1A;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 195, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .heading-main {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #00C3FF;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .form-label {
      color: #EAEAEA;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #1976D2;
      border: none;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #00C3FF;
      color: #0D0D0D;
    }

    input[type="date"] {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
    }

    input[type="date"]::placeholder {
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-8 main-container text-center">
        <h1 class="heading-main">COSMOS DAILY</h1>
        <p>Explore the universe with Cosmos Daily, your daily dose of breathtaking astronomical images and insights from NASA.</p>
        <p>Each day, we feature a different photograph of our universe, accompanied by a detailed explanation of its significance and context.</p>
        <p>From distant galaxies and nebulae to planets, moons, and space missions â€” Cosmos Daily helps you explore the cosmos one day at a time.</p>

        <form action="/info" method="post" class="mt-4">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="date" class="form-label fs-5">Select a Date</label>
            <input type="date" id="date" name="date" class="form-control form-control-lg w-50 mx-auto" required>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Go</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
